..TEXT:
It was sunrise at Jerusalem midnight in Spain
(where Libra the sign opposite to Aries would be on the meridian)
and noon in India; it was, therefore, sunset at the base of the
Mount of Purgatory (see diagrams on pp. 34 and 35).  But there
was still an interval before sunset at the height the poets had
reached (^cf.~ above, Canto.vii. ^v.~ 12).  -- See diagram on p.
103.
